---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"

import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro"
import TechnicalDivider from "../components/TechnicalDivider.astro"
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Joshua Jadulco"
  description="Technical profile - Full Stack Web Developer with expertise in Laravel, Vue, and modern web technologies"
>
  <main class="wrapper stack gap-12">
    <section class="stack gap-8">
      <Hero
        title="ABOUT_PROFILE"
        tagline="Technical profile - Background, experience, and technology stack analysis"
        align="start"
      />

      <div class="about-content stack gap-12">
        <div class="content-card">
          <TechnicalDivider title="BACKGROUND_PROFILE" />
          <div class="card-body stack gap-4">
            <p>
              Results-driven Senior Laravel Developer with 5+ years of experience architecting and delivering
              scalable web applications for enterprise clients. Specialized in full-stack Laravel development
              with deep expertise in the Laravel ecosystem, including Eloquent ORM, Service Container,
              Laravel Queues, Middleware pipelines, and advanced design patterns. Proven track record of
              leading cross-functional teams, optimizing application performance, and implementing robust
              CI/CD pipelines that reduce deployment time and improve code quality.
            </p>
            <p>
              I architect and develop enterprise-grade Laravel applications utilizing advanced OOP design
              patterns including Repository, Factory, Observer, and Strategy patterns. I leverage Laravel's
              Eloquent ORM with relationships, eager loading, and query optimization to handle complex data
              models. I implement Service Container dependency injection, custom Service Providers, and
              Middleware pipelines for scalable application architecture. I utilize Laravel Queues with
              Redis and database drivers for background job processing, and Laravel Horizon for real-time
              queue monitoring and management.
            </p>
            <p>
              I specialize in Laravel ecosystem tools including Laravel Nova for custom admin dashboards,
              Laravel Scout for Algolia and Meilisearch full-text search integration, Laravel Socialite
              for OAuth authentication with multiple providers, and Laravel Sanctum for API authentication.
              I optimize application performance through query optimization, Redis caching, opcode caching
              with OPcache, database indexing, and Laravel's caching layer with tags and atomic locks.
              I implement comprehensive API development using Laravel's API resources, API versioning,
              rate limiting, and RESTful architecture patterns.
            </p>
            <p>
              I implement Test Driven Development (TDD) and Behavior Driven Development (BDD) practices
              using PHPUnit, Pest, and Laravel Dusk for comprehensive test coverage. I write unit tests,
              feature tests, and browser tests with mocking, test doubles, and database transactions
              for isolated testing. I integrate automated testing into CI/CD pipelines with GitHub Actions,
              achieving 90%+ code coverage and enabling continuous deployment workflows. I utilize Laravel's
              testing helpers, factories, seeders, and HTTP testing for rapid test development.
            </p>
            <p>
              I lead DevOps initiatives using Docker and Docker Compose for containerized Laravel
              environments with PHP-FPM, Nginx, Redis, and MySQL. I automate CI/CD pipelines for
              automated testing, building, and deployment to staging and production environments.
              I manage Linux server infrastructure with Ubuntu and Debian, implementing deployment
              automation, log rotation, SSL certificates, and environment provisioning using Ansible
              and Bash scripting. I leverage AWS services including EC2, S3, RDS, CloudFront, and
              Elastic Load Balancing for scalable cloud infrastructure and high availability.
            </p>
            <p>
              I practice Agile and Scrum methodologies as a team lead and senior developer, facilitating
              sprint planning, daily standups, sprint reviews, and retrospectives. I create detailed user
              stories with acceptance criteria and definition of done, manage sprint backlogs with velocity
              tracking, and mentor junior developers in Laravel best practices and coding standards.
              I collaborate with stakeholders, product managers, and UX designers to translate business
              requirements into technical specifications and deliverables using Jira, Confluence, and
              Azure DevOps for project tracking and documentation.
            </p>
            <p>
              I have extensive experience with enterprise SDLC methodologies including Waterfall for
              regulated industries and hybrid Agile-Waterfall approaches. I perform requirements gathering,
              technical specification documentation, system architecture design, and database schema design
              for complex enterprise applications. I conduct code reviews, implement coding standards,
              and maintain comprehensive technical documentation for API endpoints, deployment procedures,
              and system architecture. I provide ongoing maintenance, security updates, and performance
              optimization for production Laravel applications serving thousands of concurrent users.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
